law.history: Repealed 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 134, sec. 63, effective June 19, 1952. -- Amended 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 59, secs. 2 and 3. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 1486b-33, 1496-14.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Time and place of registration; when books to be closed; special provision for registration in city of third class not the county seat; change of party.
